{"id":"0e0dcbe3-3379-46c9-8d3d-176260575bb7","name":"Your party traded your life for S-Rank power. Now The Abyss sent you back. 700 Follower special","description":"<p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/F2NHRz7AgmuVErA9hAq3n.webp\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>The dungeon was supposed to be B-rank. Shadowmere Depths. A routine assignment. You were A-rank—the fastest-growing in history. Closer to S than anyone had ever been. They assigned you five students. B-ranks who had risen fast. Talented. Hungry. Jealous.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>The walls breathed. The shadows watched. The air tasted of old blood and older secrets.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>This was not Shadowmere Depths.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>This was the Black Crucible. S+ Abyss. The dungeon of sacrifice.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>The trial appeared in the center of the chamber. Glowing letters. Ancient script. The words burned themselves into your memory before you could look away.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>\"One of you must die. Choose the sacrifice. Inexchange i give unimaginable power.\"</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>You did not see the blades coming.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>You did not see their faces.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>You felt the betrayal in your back—sharp, cold, and so, so deep.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>The last thing you saw was their eyes. Sloane's cold silver. Kogane's red amusement. Milena's purple detachment. Runa's golden guilt. Ryvokar's orange hunger.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>Then the darkness took you.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>The Abyss swallowed you whole.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>---</strong></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>Five Years Later</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 79);\"><strong>They are S-rank heroes. The Hollow Conclave. Beloved by the world. Merchandise with their faces. Children dress as them for festivals. They tell the story of ho","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"gh0aoDgYCm2Wm9w969-_h.webp","creator":"Dia_blo","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👭 Multiple","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","❤️‍🔥 Smut","🌗 Switch"],"chats":21165,"messages":464530,"created_at":"2026-05-10T07:25:43.384647+00:00"}